originalText.text: I have known Ms. Cistaro since we began trying cases in Miami back in the early 2000's. In her early years she showed great promise as a strong advocate for her clients and a formidable trial attorney.  Over the years I have seen her grow to become a tough State and Federal attorney.  She will not hesitate to fight the government and get you the results you need. She will never back away from a trial.  We have worked cases together and I know she cares about results for her clients.  Experience and a strong work ethic count and Jacqueline Cistaro will fight hard to get you the best results possible.

originalText.text: Jacqueline is just amazing. Not only is she intelligent, motivated, hard working and GREAT at what she does, but she is also kind, compassionate, and non judgmental. I needed her assistance recently for a family member and she responded promptly, answered all of my questions, and made me feel at ease. She had the ability to quickly access her national network and arrange for my family member to meet with multiple attorneys across the country within an hour. I just love her! She met ALL of my expectations, and more!
